data.description: Welcome to the Neighborhood!! You'll love this charming 55 and older golf community of Sun City, boasting 7 Rec Centers, 8 golf courses, and a plethora of clubs & activities. Experience the ultimate easy living lifestyle in this Del Webb Community. Your home comes with many upgrades and over $21,000 in renovations including Kitchen remodel, new roof, and new door. Also includes a 2-car garage with cabinets. Expansive laundry room, eat-in kitchen, formal Dining Room, plus a bonus room ideal for a home office, a sewing room, or card room. The bedrooms are spacious with vanity, walk-in closet, and walk-in shower. Step outside and enjoy the warm weather. Have coffee in either the front or back patios.  Your home is surrounded by lush green grass and shade trees. This home is a MUST see.
